  <Placemark>
   <name>Child Abduction Emergency issued October 25 at 8:49AM CDT by NWS St Louis MO</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_unknown</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>CAELSX

The following message is transmitted at the request of the
Illinois State Police.

At the request of the Riverdale police department, the Illinois
AMBER Alert notification system has been activated.

FOUR CHILDREN WERE ABDUCTED FROM 1 3 6 0 9 SOUTH LOWE AVENUE,
RIVERDALE, ILLINOIS AROUND 1:37 THIS MORNING.

NOLAN HILL IS A BLACK 7 YEAR OLD BOY, WHO WEIGHS 54 POUNDS AND
HAS BROWN EYES AND BLACK HAIR. NOLAN IS WEARING BLACK T SHIRT AND
JEANS.

NOVA HILL IS A BLACK 7 YEAR OLD GIRL, WHO WEIGHS 64 POUNDS
AND HAS BROWN EYES AND BLACK HAIR. NOVA IS WEARING A BLUE JACKET
AND BLUE JEANS.

NOAH HILL IS A BLACK 8 YEAR OLD BOY, WHO WEIGHS 60 POUNDS AND HAS
BROWN EYES AND BLACK HAIR. NOAH IS WEARING A GREEN HOODIE, BLACK
PANTS AND BLUE SHOES.

NIA HILL IS A BLACK 10 YEAR OLD GIRL, WHO WEIGHS 90 POUNDS AND
HAS BROWN EYES AND BLACK BRAIDED PONYTAIL HAIR. NIA IS WEARING AN
ORANGE T SHIRT AND BLACK JOGGERS.

THE CHILDREN WERE IN THE BACK SEAT WHEN AUSTIN BELL A 30 YEAR OLD
BLACK MALE WAS OBSERVED DRIVING OFF IN THE VEHICLE. THE VEHICLE
IS A SILVER 2010 ACURA M D X WITH ILLINOIS LICENSE F E 6 0 6 1 9.

ANYONE WITH INFORMATION SHOULD CALL 9 1 1.</Snippet>
