   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Southeast winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt,
rough bay waters, and seas 5 to 8 ft.

* WHERE...Portions of Gulf of America.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM CDT Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The Advisory may need to get extended
through Saturday night for the Gulf Waters as seas may be slow
to decrease.</Snippet>
